{"type": "article", "id": 30804, "title": "带无线充电托盘的扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809213631wNQYuqRM2kfHcCDJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>时尚的家电设计与无线充电技术之间的关系越发紧密，在 <a href=\"http://blond.cc/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blond</a> 工作室的总监 James Melia 看来，尽管有不少电器品牌已经推出了无线充电装置，它们的设计重心都更偏向于科技而忽略了产品与居家环境的契合。他领导的工作室最近就推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://blond.cc/work/duo-speaker/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Duo</a> 的家电，包含一个便携式圆柱形扬声器和配套的无线充电托盘。和市面上其他同类产品不同，Blond 特意没有选择塑料制作托盘，而是使用了可丽耐人造石（Corian），这种富有触感的材质和简约的外型使 Duo 可以很好地融入室内环境当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809213930K4kcsEjbAHgaY7QJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608092139296Wx1ptoSX4Vnak8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809213930aipeZXrS4sCd7RPy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809213931aqf5VbNL9ruUTBDs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}